des:
Tube Smart Home is a home automation platform for curtains and blinds. It is a solution that allows you to control your environment in a simple and elegant way.

Through the Tube Smart Hub and the Tube app you can control and create scenes for your curtains and blinds equipped with Tube motors.

Enabling the Tube skill you sync the scenes created in the Tube app with Alexa and gain even more freedom! Just say Alexa!

To take advantage, you will need to connect Alexa to your Tube products by following these simple steps:

 01. Download the "Tube" app from your app store;
 02. Register your Tube account using an email address;
 03. Sync your Tube Smart Hub;
 04. Configure your devices (curtains and blinds);
 05. Create scenes for your devices;
 06. Download the Amazon "Alexa" app from your app store;
 07. Configure your Alexa device in the app;
 08. Look for the skill "Tube Smart Home" in the Skills tab of the Alexa application;
 09. Click on "Activate for Use" and you will be redirected to the login screen;
 10. Enter your account details and password.
 11. Ready! The configuration is finished;
